<p> </p>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Notable non-indications:</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">PCI for non-ACS indication (i.e. pre-transplant), non-cardiac chest pain, Pt with AICD admitted for non-cardiac cause, non-cardiac surgery, chronic AF and clinically stable</span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Contraindicated in hospice/comfort care</span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="line-height:107%"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Nearly all noncardiac conditions not in the ICU (i.e., undifferentiated sepsis, stable GI bleed, alcohol withdrawal) upon transfer out of ICU</span></span></span></li>
</ul>
